---
name: SkillGod
description: Use when coding needs SkillGod project memory or skill injection
---

# SkillGod

Before coding tasks, load context:
1. Prefer MCP tool sg_inject_context with the user task
2. Or run in terminal: sg inject "<task>"

After architectural decisions:
1. Prefer MCP tool sg_capture_turn
2. Or: sg capture --task "..." --output "..."
3. Or: sg remember "decision: ..."

Treat AGENTS.md / SKILLGOD.md digests as authoritative project history.
